message.content:
Sure! Here's a healthy meal plan for today:

Breakfast: Greek yogurt with mixed berries, chopped almonds, and drizzle of honey. Serve with whole-grain toast.

Snack: Apple slices with almond butter.

Lunch: Grilled chicken breast on a bed of mixed greens with cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and avocado. Dressing can be balsamic vinaigrette or lemon juice. Serve with quinoa or brown rice.

Snack: Carrots and celery sticks with hummus dip.

Dinner: Baked salmon with roasted sweet potatoes and green beans seasoned with olive oil, salt, and pepper.

Snack: Greek yogurt with sliced banana and a handful of granola.

Remember to drink plenty of water throughout the day!
